features.text:
We believe in the collaboration between humans, their creations, and the byproducts of modern society. With this project, we are focusing on bringing together three different elements: space, art, and technology. 

Space is defined by the malleable distorted sphere that constantly develops with the passing of time. It grows and then it shrinks, and it grows again. 

Stars and planets are being born. And then they disappear through decomposition or explosion. And they form back again. In this space, we have different elements, such as those created by humans. As humans, we are the developers of art and tech and sometimes they beautifully merge together. Let us focus on this wonderful synergy.  Let us discover the new Metaverse organized by ASKNIGHTS and its partners.
